WEBVTT

02:39.960 --> 02:41.200
Officer He.

02:41.280 --> 02:43.120
Honey. One mutton rice noodle.

02:43.200 --> 02:44.400
-Extra coriander.
-Alright.

02:45.200 --> 02:46.600
To go. Make it fast.

02:46.680 --> 02:48.400
Officer He. We haven't seen you in ages.

02:48.480 --> 02:50.520
The criminal department
is busier than the station?

02:50.600 --> 02:52.320
I'll be back in three days.

02:52.400 --> 02:55.600
That's good. That's good.
We're all eager to have you back.

02:56.480 --> 02:59.560
Officer He.
There's a newcomer at the station.

02:59.640 --> 03:00.880
Officer… Officer Qu.

03:01.480 --> 03:04.320
We've never seen him smile.
Difficult person.

03:05.440 --> 03:07.640
Tell everyone to be at ease.

03:07.720 --> 03:10.800
Once I'm back,
I'll get that poker face out of here.

03:11.320 --> 03:13.720
Wait. One more noodle. No coriander.

03:13.800 --> 03:15.800
Alright. One more noodle. No coriander.

03:15.880 --> 03:17.240
-Alright.
-I'm on it.

03:18.240 --> 03:19.160
POLICE CODE OF CONDUCT
ON UNIFORM AND APPEARANCE

03:19.240 --> 03:21.680
I haven't slept for days.

03:21.760 --> 03:22.600
CONFERENCE ROOM

03:22.680 --> 03:24.040
Seriously.

03:25.720 --> 03:27.280
Good to see you, guys.

03:28.520 --> 03:29.400
Have one.

03:29.920 --> 03:31.080
I don't smoke. Thanks.

03:33.960 --> 03:35.200
Hi.

03:37.760 --> 03:38.720
Writing notes?

03:39.400 --> 03:41.040
-Let's eat after this.
-Okay.

03:46.120 --> 03:46.960
Get up.

03:49.520 --> 03:52.000
Same old rules. Long story short.

03:52.840 --> 03:54.200
Last night,

03:54.280 --> 03:57.600
there was a major burglary
at the Dongshan Mine.

03:57.680 --> 04:00.800
Valuable items
and important materials were lost.

04:00.880 --> 04:03.200
My higher-ups were on my neck all night.

04:03.800 --> 04:04.880
From now on,

04:04.960 --> 04:09.920
whoever doesn't have important tasks
will join the Special Task Force.

04:10.000 --> 04:12.080
Tan. Give out the materials.

04:14.880 --> 04:17.519
-Big cases? Ours?
-You in?

04:21.040 --> 04:22.280
Captain.

04:24.160 --> 04:26.560
Of course, we should
prioritize the big case.

04:27.360 --> 04:28.520
Captain Feng.

04:31.520 --> 04:32.360
Fangxu.

04:32.960 --> 04:34.600
You already got ideas?

04:34.680 --> 04:36.160
Tell us about it.

04:36.240 --> 04:40.400
Everyone here will get to hear
the ideas of a PPSUC graduate.

04:48.080 --> 04:49.080
Captain Feng.

04:49.720 --> 04:52.080
The missing persons case
I'm working on is also quite urgent.

04:54.440 --> 04:56.320
Seriously?

04:59.200 --> 05:00.480
Seriously?

05:01.960 --> 05:03.000
Yuanhang.

05:04.080 --> 05:06.840
Has the case in Yuanlongli been filed?

05:07.680 --> 05:08.520
Not yet.

05:08.600 --> 05:09.920
How long have you been on this?

05:12.040 --> 05:13.120
Four days.

05:13.200 --> 05:15.480
They've been investigating
around the clock,

05:15.560 --> 05:19.040
as busy as bees, 24 hours non-stop.

05:23.240 --> 05:24.640
Yuanhang.

05:24.720 --> 05:26.880
It's been four days.

05:26.960 --> 05:29.520
We can't file a case
without finding the person.

05:30.200 --> 05:32.000
But based on what we know,

05:32.080 --> 05:34.680
this case is highly likely
to develop into a murder.

05:35.280 --> 05:38.080
What makes you think
it's going to be a murder?

05:38.680 --> 05:41.760
Is that based on proof or your intuition?

05:45.360 --> 05:46.600
Captain Feng.

05:47.880 --> 05:48.720
On probability.

05:50.160 --> 05:52.960
Approximately 25% of missing persons cases
are ultimately classified as homicides.

05:53.040 --> 05:56.480
For every four missing people,
one dies of unnatural causes.

05:56.560 --> 06:00.480
And now we've passed the golden 72 hours
for finding the missing person.

06:00.560 --> 06:03.880
Every extra day means more danger
to the missing person.

06:08.360 --> 06:09.280
That's all.

06:20.960 --> 06:23.880
Captain, this kid is a bookworm.

06:23.960 --> 06:25.640
Please don't mind him.

06:25.720 --> 06:27.400
You think I don't know that?

06:27.480 --> 06:30.520
I was also annoyingly stubborn
when I was young.

06:32.080 --> 06:34.240
This kid is persistent.

06:34.320 --> 06:36.120
He'll make a good officer.

06:37.360 --> 06:38.840
But then again,

06:41.320 --> 06:43.800
you are also to blame
for his stubbornness.

06:44.440 --> 06:46.360
You've been mentoring him for days.

06:46.440 --> 06:47.800
Is this how you train him?

06:47.880 --> 06:49.640
How can I mentor a college graduate?

06:49.720 --> 06:52.120
Besides, you never said
that I'd be his mentor.

06:54.360 --> 06:57.920
Isn't he sure that it's going
to turn into a murder?

06:58.000 --> 07:01.520
How about this? Keep an eye on your area.

07:01.600 --> 07:03.920
Transfer Ran Fangxu
to the Special Task Force.

07:04.000 --> 07:06.440
Transfer him here to keep defying you?

07:06.520 --> 07:09.360
Also, we're not allowed
to work cases alone.

07:09.440 --> 07:10.480
How about this, Captain?

07:10.560 --> 07:13.480
Give us an official order and a deadline.

07:13.560 --> 07:15.280
This way, he'll have no complaints. Okay?

07:16.560 --> 07:18.240
To be honest, I believe

07:18.320 --> 07:22.520
that a missing person matters more
than some lost items.

07:28.200 --> 07:30.640
Fine. How many days do you need?

07:30.720 --> 07:31.640
Three days.

07:31.720 --> 07:34.360
After three days, I'll bring that kid
to the Special Task Force.

07:41.480 --> 07:42.640
Captain.

07:50.320 --> 07:52.040
When are you going back
to the police station?

07:55.640 --> 07:56.520
Also in three days.

07:59.000 --> 08:00.600
Sneaky fox.

08:02.280 --> 08:03.320
I…

08:05.160 --> 08:07.360
There's nothing in it for me.

08:07.440 --> 08:08.800
I did it all for you.

08:10.480 --> 08:13.200
Thank you, Officer He.

08:13.280 --> 08:14.960
For what?

08:15.040 --> 08:17.880
You should thank Captain Feng.
He values talent.

08:17.960 --> 08:21.320
Also, stop addressing me so formally.

08:22.520 --> 08:24.040
What should I call you?

08:26.280 --> 08:28.080
Our partnership will end soon.

08:28.160 --> 08:30.920
I won't take advantage of you
and make you call me "sir".

08:32.000 --> 08:33.320
Just call me He.

08:38.320 --> 08:39.799
He.

08:39.880 --> 08:42.440
I will do my best
to avoid delaying your return.

08:47.920 --> 08:50.200
To be honest,
I have some selfish intentions.

08:50.280 --> 08:52.720
This case has almost become a joke.

08:52.800 --> 08:54.280
I can't go back empty-handed.

08:55.120 --> 08:58.160
That's enough. Dig in. Dig in.

08:58.240 --> 08:59.720
Clean it up afterward.

09:12.480 --> 09:14.000
You like coriander too?

09:14.560 --> 09:16.000
Have this. I'll have this.

09:24.200 --> 09:26.160
It's a bit too much.

09:46.680 --> 09:50.000
The case of Dongshan Mine
is the real deal.

09:50.080 --> 09:52.680
But you're only interested
in a minor case.

10:02.920 --> 10:05.080
My parents also went missing.

10:06.760 --> 10:08.720
At first, they said it was nothing.

10:10.480 --> 10:12.440
But later, they found…

10:28.240 --> 10:29.520
their bodies.

10:47.240 --> 10:49.760
We have three days. We have time.

10:56.320 --> 10:57.280
Okay.

11:11.960 --> 11:13.320
Wait.

11:13.400 --> 11:16.040
MUSE FOOT MASSAGE, OWNER: ZHAO HONGMEI

11:18.000 --> 11:19.520
MUSE FOOT MASSAGE, OWNER: ZHAO HONGMEI

11:20.120 --> 11:21.720
How did I forget about her?

11:21.800 --> 11:26.920
MUSE FOOT MASSAGE

11:33.040 --> 11:34.080
So annoying.

11:43.200 --> 11:45.200
Don't slam the door.

11:51.320 --> 11:54.320
We have zero customers
after the police visited.

11:55.000 --> 11:56.720
Not even a fly flew in.

12:03.120 --> 12:04.760
It's all because of Mengmeng.

12:05.840 --> 12:06.880
Listen.

12:06.960 --> 12:09.200
No one is allowed
to mention Mengmeng again.

12:10.000 --> 12:12.680
Do not gossip about her to anyone.

12:12.760 --> 12:14.200
You hear me?

12:17.320 --> 12:18.360
You hear me?

12:18.440 --> 12:20.760
Yeah.

12:21.600 --> 12:23.720
Lili. Get a perm.

12:23.800 --> 12:27.040
Look at your hair.
It's like a pot of plants.

12:27.120 --> 12:28.560
Ms. Zhao.

12:28.640 --> 12:30.680
I need money for that.

12:30.760 --> 12:32.160
You haven't paid me this month.

12:39.360 --> 12:42.600
Why are you staring at me?
Do I have money on my face?

12:44.120 --> 12:46.160
Still staring? Go get a perm.

12:50.200 --> 12:54.320
QINGSONG CEMENT CONNECTS YOU AND ME

12:55.280 --> 12:59.800
MUSE FOOT MASSAGE

13:21.160 --> 13:22.480
I don't know Mengmeng so well.

13:22.560 --> 13:24.560
I don't know what exactly happened to her.

13:24.640 --> 13:25.880
What happened?

13:30.160 --> 13:33.320
If I remember correctly,
you wanted to say something that night.

13:33.400 --> 13:34.880
No one picked her.

13:34.960 --> 13:37.000
She didn't earn anything,
so she stopped coming.

13:37.640 --> 13:38.480
Why did she miss work?

13:39.080 --> 13:40.120
I don't know.

13:43.800 --> 13:46.480
Officer, stop pushing me.

13:46.560 --> 13:48.400
I… I really don't know.

13:48.480 --> 13:50.840
I have things to do. Can I leave now?

13:50.920 --> 13:51.760
No.

13:52.800 --> 13:54.040
Did Zhao Hongmei threaten you?

13:55.160 --> 13:57.520
I can arrest her
if she's hiding something.

14:02.320 --> 14:05.920
Rest assured. The information
you provide will be kept confidential.

14:06.000 --> 14:08.400
-We're just trying to find Mengmeng.
-Yeah.

14:15.880 --> 14:20.520
Actually, Mengmeng had some bad luck
right before she disappeared.

14:20.600 --> 14:21.640
Bad luck?

14:24.600 --> 14:28.560
Speaking of which,
she took the hit for me.

14:34.640 --> 14:38.880
MUSE FOOT MASSAGE

14:38.960 --> 14:40.120
Mr. Song.

14:40.720 --> 14:42.040
Mr. Song.

14:42.600 --> 14:44.600
You finally came to inspect our work.

14:44.680 --> 14:46.120
Be careful.

14:48.160 --> 14:50.960
Our young ladies have missed you so much.

14:52.040 --> 14:53.160
Wait.

14:54.120 --> 14:54.960
Briefcase.

14:55.600 --> 14:56.680
Hurry.

15:00.160 --> 15:04.280
MUSE FOOT MASSAGE

15:06.320 --> 15:10.480
Welcome, Mr. Song.

15:10.560 --> 15:12.160
-Mei.
-Yes?

15:12.240 --> 15:14.480
I've traveled everywhere.

15:14.560 --> 15:16.360
This is the best place for me.

15:16.440 --> 15:19.320
Wherever you say is nice,
that's the nicest place.

15:22.000 --> 15:24.400
Don't just stand there.
Hurry up and get around.

15:24.480 --> 15:26.840
Get closer to Mr. Song.

15:28.960 --> 15:31.400
Go ahead. Go ahead.

15:38.720 --> 15:42.120
Mr. Song. Lili. Get him in.

15:42.720 --> 15:46.080
How dare you snatch my things?

15:47.880 --> 15:51.200
I'll break your other leg, too.

16:00.160 --> 16:02.040
Who are you?

16:02.120 --> 16:04.000
Mr. Song, I'm Lili.

16:04.920 --> 16:06.080
QINGSONG CEMENT

16:07.360 --> 16:09.280
Who said you could touch my briefcase?

16:09.360 --> 16:11.200
The essential oil might drip on it.

16:11.280 --> 16:12.760
Who said you could touch my briefcase?

16:12.840 --> 16:13.800
I paid for that.

16:13.880 --> 16:15.640
Who said you could touch my briefcase?

16:15.720 --> 16:18.640
How dare you touch my briefcase?

16:18.720 --> 16:20.080
-How dare you!
-Mr. Song.

16:20.160 --> 16:21.520
What are you doing? What are you doing?

16:21.600 --> 16:23.240
Go away. Go away.

16:23.320 --> 16:25.160
Why are you angry with that dumb girl?

16:25.240 --> 16:26.840
Don't be mad. I'll get you someone else.

16:26.920 --> 16:28.360
Mengmeng.

16:28.440 --> 16:30.240
Mengmeng is very sweet.
She'll make you happy.

16:30.320 --> 16:32.520
Mengmeng. Hurry.

16:34.400 --> 16:37.480
Come on. Mr. Song, this is Mengmeng.
Serve him well.

16:45.800 --> 16:48.640
That briefcase says "Qingsong Cement".

16:48.720 --> 16:51.040
-So Mr. Song is…
-Song Qingsong.

16:51.800 --> 16:54.360
There is only one Mr. Song in Weiyang.

16:54.440 --> 16:57.840
Hundreds of people gathered for a fight
outside the cement factory a few days ago.

16:57.920 --> 17:00.040
It was because of him
and Cripple Du of the steel factory.

17:00.960 --> 17:03.640
Those two are known to be enemies.

17:05.000 --> 17:07.119
SONG QINGSONG

17:07.720 --> 17:10.480
Song Qingsong met Xu Meng.
What happened next?

17:11.119 --> 17:14.760
I thought Mr. Song could calm down
after he saw Mengmeng.

17:14.839 --> 17:16.480
But Mengmeng started screaming in there.

17:16.560 --> 17:18.680
And Mr. Song hit her even harder.

17:20.240 --> 17:21.160
Why?

17:22.319 --> 17:25.359
I think it was still
because of that briefcase.

17:25.440 --> 17:27.359
-How dare you!
-Mr. Song, spare me.

17:27.440 --> 17:28.840
Mr. Song, spare me.

17:28.920 --> 17:30.000
Shut up.

17:30.080 --> 17:31.520
-Still won't admit it?
-I am sorry.

17:31.600 --> 17:33.520
Spare me.

17:33.600 --> 17:36.240
I can make you disappear from Weiyang.

17:36.320 --> 17:37.440
You hear me?

17:38.200 --> 17:40.720
I can make you disappear.

17:40.800 --> 17:41.760
I'm sorry.

17:41.840 --> 17:43.800
I'm sorry. Spare me.

17:43.880 --> 17:45.600
-Still crying?
-Spare me.

17:45.680 --> 17:47.040
Spare me.

17:47.120 --> 17:48.680
Still crying, huh?

17:48.760 --> 17:50.080
I can make you disappear!

17:51.960 --> 17:53.320
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

17:53.400 --> 17:54.560
Spare me.

17:54.640 --> 17:56.640
-Still crying?
-Spare me.

17:56.720 --> 17:59.880
Mr. Song kept beating her in that room.

17:59.960 --> 18:02.680
Eventually, she went silent.

18:03.720 --> 18:06.200
Song Qingsong said he'd made
Xu Meng disappear from Weiyang?

18:06.280 --> 18:07.320
Yeah.

18:08.640 --> 18:10.360
He kept repeating those words.

18:10.440 --> 18:12.000
I heard him clearly.

18:12.960 --> 18:15.000
Any idea what's in that briefcase?

18:15.080 --> 18:18.600
White papers. A thick stack.

18:18.680 --> 18:20.920
It hurt so much when he hit me with those.

18:21.960 --> 18:24.040
Papers? Not money?

18:25.280 --> 18:26.200
Not money.

18:26.280 --> 18:28.440
Maybe for rich people,

18:29.280 --> 18:31.280
paper is money,

18:32.440 --> 18:35.160
and money sometimes is just paper.

18:37.000 --> 18:39.080
They say, "Life is as fragile as paper."

18:40.840 --> 18:42.360
People like us

18:44.040 --> 18:45.680
are worth less than some papers.

18:56.560 --> 18:59.320
Did Song Qingsong and Xu Meng
know each other?

19:00.040 --> 19:02.400
Mengmeng and I used to work in Pattia.

19:03.400 --> 19:06.640
Mr. Song often came
and asked for Mengmeng.

19:07.280 --> 19:09.320
He wanted to keep her as his mistress.

19:09.400 --> 19:10.760
But she turned him down.

19:11.880 --> 19:14.280
That's why she got beaten
and sent to the hospital.

19:15.240 --> 19:16.720
Didn't your boss do anything about it?

19:16.800 --> 19:18.040
She dared not.

19:18.120 --> 19:21.280
Mr. Song rented her the place.
What could she do?

19:24.880 --> 19:29.120
The 18th floor of New York Block
is Song Qingsong's property?

19:30.560 --> 19:32.720
He also owns the dorms downstairs.

19:32.800 --> 19:35.200
Did Xu Meng tell you
why she turned him down?

19:35.280 --> 19:37.600
She just didn't want to be a mistress.

19:38.880 --> 19:40.160
Ms. Zhao said

19:41.200 --> 19:43.400
that Mengmeng owed a lot of money.

19:54.240 --> 19:57.920
QINGSONG CEMENT CONNECTS YOU AND ME

19:59.920 --> 20:01.480
I just got back from a business trip.

20:02.320 --> 20:03.240
Mr. Liu.

20:04.040 --> 20:06.600
What I have at hand
is absolutely reliable.

20:06.680 --> 20:09.320
I'll show you when the time is right.

20:10.880 --> 20:13.440
But right now, I'm a bit short of funds.

20:14.120 --> 20:16.480
If you're willing to help,

20:16.560 --> 20:19.280
you can wait
to make loads of money with me.

20:19.360 --> 20:20.360
Get back to me.

20:25.080 --> 20:29.400
MISSING PERSON

20:29.480 --> 20:32.400
MUSE

20:32.480 --> 20:34.360
"Disappeared from Weiyang."

20:35.040 --> 20:36.960
Doesn't that sound familiar?

20:38.520 --> 20:41.440
You're talking about the guy
in the video rental shop?

20:45.040 --> 20:46.880
That guy was drunk. It doesn't count.

20:47.640 --> 20:49.680
Song Qingsong has plenty of women.

20:49.760 --> 20:52.480
Why would he be so serious
about a massage lady?

20:52.560 --> 20:55.320
Besides, Wolfie only killed chickens.

20:55.400 --> 20:58.440
Even if Song Qingsong hired Wolfie,
the murder didn't happen.

20:59.040 --> 21:00.560
What if he hired someone else?

21:01.680 --> 21:05.000
Both Xu Meng and Lili were beaten
because they touched his briefcase.

21:05.600 --> 21:07.880
Why was only Xu Meng threatened?

21:09.280 --> 21:10.320
And the briefcase.

21:10.400 --> 21:13.720
Song Qingsong didn't even trust his driver

21:13.800 --> 21:16.640
and carried it with him
to the massage place.

21:17.640 --> 21:19.920
What was in that briefcase?

21:20.000 --> 21:24.680
A business owner usually carries
important documents,

21:24.760 --> 21:26.960
checks, and bank drafts.

21:29.520 --> 21:30.440
He.

21:31.200 --> 21:34.920
Why does it sound like you're trying
to defend Song Qingsong?

21:36.080 --> 21:37.400
Really?

21:37.480 --> 21:38.320
Why?

21:40.760 --> 21:45.080
Song Qingsong and Cripple Du take turns
to be the richest man in Weiyang.

21:45.160 --> 21:47.520
They pay huge amounts of tax.

21:47.600 --> 21:49.520
Even the authorities
have to show them some respect.

21:49.600 --> 21:51.040
You know what I mean?

21:51.120 --> 21:53.120
What does it have to do with the case?

21:53.200 --> 21:56.400
We lack proof to tie them to this case.

21:56.480 --> 21:58.960
That's why we can't act rashly
towards Song Qingsong.

22:05.600 --> 22:06.600
I see.

22:06.680 --> 22:07.880
Good.

22:07.960 --> 22:09.400
You're afraid of Song Qingsong.

22:10.720 --> 22:12.720
I'm afraid of Song Qingsong?

22:12.800 --> 22:14.840
I'm a police officer.
Why would I be afraid?

22:14.920 --> 22:17.720
We fight the bad people
and protect the good.

22:17.800 --> 22:20.280
We're not sure that Song Qingsong
is a bad guy, right?

22:20.360 --> 22:23.760
He put a woman in the hospital.
How is he a good guy?

22:25.280 --> 22:28.000
Song Qingsong is known
to be a sneaky fox in Weiyang.

22:28.080 --> 22:31.320
We can't just approach him
with Lili's testimony.

22:31.400 --> 22:33.040
We may alert him.

22:33.760 --> 22:35.440
We must form a strategy.

22:37.520 --> 22:38.440
Like what?

22:43.400 --> 22:47.360
Well… the strategy
is to not scare off the target,

22:47.440 --> 22:49.600
but also not come away with nothing.

22:49.680 --> 22:50.760
So…

22:55.880 --> 22:57.080
So…

22:58.880 --> 23:00.160
I need to call someone.

23:00.240 --> 23:02.560
Then I'll tell you more
about the strategy.

23:02.640 --> 23:03.560
Don't be impulsive.

23:07.240 --> 23:08.360
What are you doing?

23:08.440 --> 23:09.640
Didn't you say that we lack proof?

23:09.720 --> 23:11.400
I'll look for evidence at Yuanlongli now.

23:12.400 --> 23:14.920
Why do you keep going to Yuanlongli?

23:15.640 --> 23:16.640
You have a girlfriend there?

23:18.920 --> 23:21.120
WEIYANG QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY

23:21.840 --> 23:22.680
Come here.

23:28.200 --> 23:29.040
Brother-in-law.

23:29.720 --> 23:30.920
Come closer.

23:37.680 --> 23:39.280
I paid you to deal with someone.

23:39.360 --> 23:41.360
This is how you handled it?

23:41.960 --> 23:43.080
I can explain, brother-in-law.

23:43.760 --> 23:44.600
Come here.

23:49.960 --> 23:51.960
I've told you so many times.
What do you call me in the factory?

23:52.040 --> 23:54.000
Mr. Song. Mr. Song.

23:54.080 --> 23:57.560
I made that woman disappear
as you told me to.

23:57.640 --> 23:59.280
I hired a hitman.

23:59.360 --> 24:01.040
She and her dad. Both gone.
Only 40,000 yuan.

24:01.120 --> 24:03.960
I told you to do it in person,
but you subcontracted it.

24:05.320 --> 24:06.160
For kickbacks?

24:06.240 --> 24:08.560
No. Absolutely not. I swear.

24:08.640 --> 24:10.160
I dare not steal a penny from you.

24:12.600 --> 24:13.760
Look at me.

24:13.840 --> 24:15.120
Okay.

24:15.720 --> 24:17.360
Is that woman really dead?

24:17.440 --> 24:18.600
Yeah.

24:19.200 --> 24:21.640
I looked into that hitman
before I hired him.

24:21.720 --> 24:24.880
He's killed several people.
He's professional.

24:29.960 --> 24:30.840
You saw it happening?

24:30.920 --> 24:34.400
Yeah. I saw it happening.
Buried in the mountains.

24:34.480 --> 24:36.000
Buried in the mountains?

24:38.360 --> 24:39.880
Why don't I believe it?

24:40.880 --> 24:42.280
Stupid woman.

24:42.920 --> 24:44.880
Writing to blackmail me?

24:50.240 --> 24:52.240
Go. Dig up the body.

24:54.040 --> 24:56.320
If she's really dead, bring me her body.

24:56.400 --> 24:57.600
Alright. Got it.

24:57.680 --> 25:01.280
If she is still alive,
you will disappear from Weiyang.

25:04.560 --> 25:06.920
PUBLIC TELEPHONE

25:08.040 --> 25:13.720
WEIYANG QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY

25:13.800 --> 25:16.960
PUBLIC TELEPHONE

25:20.400 --> 25:22.120
-Hello.
-What's up?

25:22.760 --> 25:23.720
Song Qingsong is back?

25:23.800 --> 25:25.080
Right.

25:25.160 --> 25:26.400
Did you get the thing?

25:26.480 --> 25:27.880
I'm not in the mood for this.

25:27.960 --> 25:29.760
I don't care if you're in the mood.

25:29.840 --> 25:30.800
Just tell me if you got it.

25:30.880 --> 25:34.160
Will you shut up?
Are you all trying to drive me crazy?

25:34.240 --> 25:37.280
Wu Shanlong. We're in the same boat.

25:37.360 --> 25:40.240
If you don't get the thing,
the boat could flip anytime.

25:40.320 --> 25:43.120
I got it. Exactly the same.

25:43.200 --> 25:44.680
It's in the safe in my house now.

25:44.760 --> 25:46.560
It's safe there. Happy now?

25:53.320 --> 25:55.320
Ma'am. Any instructions?

25:55.400 --> 25:58.040
My mom is not feeling well today.
She can't cook.

25:58.120 --> 25:59.960
Huh? Is she okay?

26:00.480 --> 26:03.280
Should I take her
to the hospital after work?

26:03.360 --> 26:05.720
Waiting for you
is like waiting for pigs to fly.

26:05.800 --> 26:07.160
I'm assigned to a business trip.

26:07.240 --> 26:09.080
Pick up Xiaohe from my mom's place.

26:09.800 --> 26:11.000
When will you be back?

26:11.080 --> 26:14.320
Should I ask my mom
to keep Xiaohe for a few days?

26:14.400 --> 26:15.560
Last time she was there,

26:15.640 --> 26:17.520
she chased mice and fell into the pigsty.

26:17.600 --> 26:18.680
The countryside is not safe.

26:18.760 --> 26:20.360
And what if there are abductors?

26:20.440 --> 26:23.320
Well, I'll take Xiaohe to our station.

26:23.400 --> 26:24.400
That's the safest place.

26:24.480 --> 26:26.920
Don't let her eat ice cream
and drink Coke when I'm away.

26:27.920 --> 26:30.480
I wouldn't do that.
I don't even drink Coke myself.

26:33.280 --> 26:34.240
Fine.

26:41.000 --> 26:43.360
Countryside. What's wrong with it?

26:44.760 --> 26:45.600
Get me another Coke.

26:45.680 --> 26:47.240
Help yourself.

27:01.400 --> 27:02.480
Kiddo.

27:03.920 --> 27:05.760
Do you want to go out to work the case?

27:07.800 --> 27:09.760
I've worked hard

27:10.280 --> 27:12.800
and made contributions
on the Yuanlongli case.

27:12.880 --> 27:16.440
I can tell Zhao Jie to hand this case
over to you tomorrow.

27:16.520 --> 27:17.880
What do you think?

27:21.800 --> 27:22.720
Tell me.

27:22.800 --> 27:26.840
How can they put someone
so talented as you on the bench?

27:26.920 --> 27:27.880
Right?

27:28.600 --> 27:30.600
Your dad is experienced.

27:30.680 --> 27:32.120
Plus your Uncle Ran.

27:32.200 --> 27:34.360
The three of us will join forces

27:34.440 --> 27:36.520
and crack this case in no time.

27:39.000 --> 27:41.960
Dad. Let me emphasize it again.

27:42.640 --> 27:45.160
Stay out of the Yuanlongli case.

27:45.240 --> 27:47.040
And stop going to Yuanlongli.

27:47.120 --> 27:48.440
Never again.

27:49.480 --> 27:51.560
Why are you so worked up?

27:53.040 --> 27:53.880
Who is it?

28:03.280 --> 28:04.120
Ran.

28:04.720 --> 28:07.800
Sir. How's the injury?

28:08.960 --> 28:11.160
It's minor. Don't worry. Come in.

28:11.240 --> 28:13.520
Kiddo. Look who's here.

28:16.840 --> 28:18.760
This kid is so rude.

28:18.840 --> 28:22.400
Your Uncle Ran is here.
Also, aren't you going to eat?

28:25.360 --> 28:26.640
Acting up again?

28:27.240 --> 28:29.760
Maybe work is stressful these days.

28:31.920 --> 28:34.400
Oh, right. Where were you?

28:34.480 --> 28:37.000
Why did you vanish when the police came?

28:39.080 --> 28:42.920
I'm just a teacher.
I shouldn't cause them trouble.

28:43.000 --> 28:44.800
Why would you say that?

28:44.880 --> 28:47.720
By order of seniority,
you're their senior.

28:50.160 --> 28:53.200
Come on. Let's talk in my room.
Come to my room.

29:38.600 --> 29:40.160
-Sir.
-Yes?

29:41.040 --> 29:43.840
All these things are about Yuanlongli?

29:44.440 --> 29:45.480
Yeah.

29:46.120 --> 29:47.960
These are my treasures.

29:48.920 --> 29:49.920
And yours.

29:56.840 --> 30:00.720
NOTEBOOK

30:02.120 --> 30:02.960
How…

30:03.040 --> 30:07.200
You walked away without a care
and left them there.

30:07.280 --> 30:09.680
They naturally became mine.

30:11.240 --> 30:12.720
Actually,

30:13.560 --> 30:15.120
I've always had a feeling.

30:16.240 --> 30:19.320
I've always felt that the missing people
in Yuanlongli in the past few years…

30:19.400 --> 30:20.080
SONG QINGSONG

30:20.160 --> 30:23.880
…were related to Xu Meng
and her father's case 18 years ago.

30:23.960 --> 30:26.240
You saw it today.

30:26.320 --> 30:29.080
A kid hid in Yuanlongli

30:29.160 --> 30:31.400
and attacked whoever he saw.

30:31.480 --> 30:33.680
Isn't it weird?

30:33.760 --> 30:36.440
Shouldn't we look into Yuanlongli?

30:41.880 --> 30:45.000
Sir, we found the kid.

30:45.080 --> 30:47.240
Just leave it to the police.

30:47.760 --> 30:49.600
We're not qualified to intervene.

30:52.280 --> 30:54.600
Yeah. We're not qualified.

30:55.520 --> 30:57.760
You left. I retired.

30:58.760 --> 31:01.960
But this is Xiaohe's first case,
after all.

31:02.720 --> 31:04.080
Xiaohe's case?

31:04.160 --> 31:05.400
Yeah.

31:05.480 --> 31:07.840
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

31:08.520 --> 31:10.680
Zhao Jie just announced it this evening.

31:16.400 --> 31:19.840
Xiaohe is still young.
This is her first case.

31:19.920 --> 31:22.560
She doesn't catch on
as fast as you did back then.

31:22.640 --> 31:24.640
This kid is way too stubborn.

31:24.720 --> 31:28.440
She clearly needs help,
but just doesn't say it.

31:29.240 --> 31:30.280
Ran.

31:30.360 --> 31:32.480
I genuinely hope

31:32.560 --> 31:35.200
that the two of us can join hands again

31:35.280 --> 31:37.080
to help Xiaohe.

31:38.280 --> 31:40.400
Rest assured. I promise

31:40.480 --> 31:45.040
I will do my best
to avoid delaying your return.

31:45.640 --> 31:46.560
Okay?

31:51.120 --> 31:52.800
Then it's settled.

31:52.880 --> 31:55.080
Let me thank you on behalf of Xiaohe.

31:59.560 --> 32:04.160
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

32:19.800 --> 32:21.080
Officer Ran.

32:21.800 --> 32:22.760
Why are you here?

32:24.840 --> 32:25.680
These are for you.

32:26.560 --> 32:28.640
Why did you buy new ones? No need.

32:28.720 --> 32:30.680
It's the least I could do.
I have to thank you.

32:30.760 --> 32:31.760
Here.

32:33.480 --> 32:35.800
Still, you didn't have
to come all the way here.

32:36.600 --> 32:38.160
Come in and have some water.

32:39.000 --> 32:41.480
No need. I have things to do.

32:46.760 --> 32:49.400
Still that thing upstairs?

32:50.000 --> 32:52.040
People have been terrified.

32:52.640 --> 32:53.880
You haven't found her?

32:55.440 --> 32:56.640
Officer Ran.

32:57.240 --> 32:58.680
Wang Xinglong said you came
to the fourth floor.

32:59.280 --> 33:00.680
Wait for me. Be right there.

33:00.760 --> 33:01.760
Okay.

33:07.360 --> 33:10.600
Right. How's the injury?

33:12.280 --> 33:13.760
It's basically healed.

33:13.840 --> 33:15.000
It won't leave a scar.

33:23.880 --> 33:26.240
Go ahead. Business first.

33:26.320 --> 33:28.480
Tell me if you need help.

33:29.280 --> 33:30.360
Thanks.

33:36.440 --> 33:37.520
Then…

33:50.120 --> 33:52.200
CASUAL SNEAKERS

34:03.440 --> 34:04.320
Officer Ran.

34:05.120 --> 34:10.639
Do you know the deal
with that woman in 415?

34:10.719 --> 34:13.120
-What about her?
-She was being kept as a mistress.

34:14.159 --> 34:15.040
True.

34:15.120 --> 34:17.880
The one who kept her was an old man.

34:17.960 --> 34:19.239
In his seventies.

34:19.320 --> 34:24.520
Last winter, the old man slipped
on the stairs and fell.

34:24.600 --> 34:26.639
Cerebral hemorrhage. He died.

34:26.719 --> 34:29.880
That apartment she lives in
belonged to that old man.

34:30.480 --> 34:35.120
But it seems that he never gave it
to that woman.

34:35.199 --> 34:38.960
Why did she do that? She's so pretty.

34:39.040 --> 34:42.560
She could have married any decent guy.

34:42.639 --> 34:44.679
Why did she pick an old man?

34:54.560 --> 34:56.520
Officer Ran. We're here.

34:58.920 --> 35:01.200
After Pattia was seized,

35:01.280 --> 35:05.240
Mr. Song gave us the keys
to these two floors

35:05.320 --> 35:07.160
and asked us to look for tenants.

35:07.240 --> 35:08.680
This half belongs to merchants.

35:09.600 --> 35:12.520
The left-hand side
used to be Pattia's dorm.

35:12.600 --> 35:13.920
Which one should we check first?

35:15.480 --> 35:19.000
QIHUANG CLINIC

35:33.720 --> 35:35.880
Raid! Raid!

35:38.960 --> 35:40.560
PRIVATE ROOM 3

35:43.280 --> 35:44.440
That one.

35:44.520 --> 35:45.360
Okay.

36:09.320 --> 36:11.080
ANSWER

36:15.280 --> 36:16.880
I DON'T BELIEVE DREAMS ARE FALSE
I DON'T BELIEVE DEATH HAS NO RETRIBUTION

36:16.960 --> 36:17.960
IF THE SEA IS DESTINED TO BURST ITS DIKES

36:18.040 --> 36:19.360
LET ALL THE BITTER WATERS
POUR INTO MY HEART

36:26.120 --> 36:27.480
MENGMENG NO.23

36:29.760 --> 36:31.600
It's their work badge in Pattia.

36:38.960 --> 36:40.680
This is Mengmeng. Do you know her?

36:41.280 --> 36:42.840
The missing ghost?

36:43.560 --> 36:45.440
A suspected missing person.

36:48.280 --> 36:49.600
I can't tell.

36:49.680 --> 36:53.160
There are 20 or 30 young ladies
coming and going here,

36:53.240 --> 36:54.880
all heavily made up.

36:54.960 --> 36:57.800
I don't recognize her without makeup.

37:01.560 --> 37:03.320
It's also a dorm next door.

37:03.400 --> 37:05.840
Someone is still living here?

37:08.080 --> 37:09.280
Worker of Pattia.

37:14.760 --> 37:16.640
In the front. Where is she?

37:17.240 --> 37:18.400
Where did she go?

37:35.960 --> 37:37.600
Don't throw my cards away.

37:37.680 --> 37:40.200
Where is the gaming machine? Take it out.

37:40.280 --> 37:42.320
Do you hear me? I'm counting to three.

37:42.400 --> 37:44.360
One. Two.

37:45.280 --> 37:46.280
Hey!

37:48.160 --> 37:49.440
How come it's you?

37:49.520 --> 37:51.240
You scared me to death.

37:56.720 --> 37:59.080
This kid plays games all day.

37:59.160 --> 38:00.560
He's ruined.

38:04.040 --> 38:05.960
-Thanks.
-I forbid him to play.

38:06.880 --> 38:11.040
Well, he hid in the corridor
and kept playing.

38:12.080 --> 38:13.360
What are you wearing?

38:13.440 --> 38:14.360
Women's clothes?

38:14.440 --> 38:15.960
You think I'll go easy on you?

38:17.920 --> 38:20.280
Ma'am, calm down.

38:20.360 --> 38:21.520
He's just a kid.

38:25.200 --> 38:27.680
-Unbelievable.
-Ma'am.

38:28.480 --> 38:29.840
These…

38:32.600 --> 38:34.400
Playing games all day long.

38:35.520 --> 38:37.640
It's summer vacation. So I'm playing.

38:37.720 --> 38:38.960
-What's the big deal?
-"What's the big deal"?

38:40.040 --> 38:43.400
Ma'am, I'm here to learn
about the missing person.

38:43.480 --> 38:46.520
They say this floor
was Pattia's staff dorm before.

38:46.600 --> 38:50.320
Pattia was seized before I moved here.

38:50.400 --> 38:54.240
Have you seen anything weird
in the building recently?

38:55.560 --> 38:58.080
The two next door moved out last month.

38:58.160 --> 38:59.480
Business was bad.

39:00.240 --> 39:03.120
The one across, 1703, is a residence.

39:03.200 --> 39:05.880
We only hear men and women
crying and shouting

39:05.960 --> 39:07.520
in the middle of the night.

39:08.120 --> 39:09.320
It's so…

39:11.040 --> 39:12.120
You know?

39:13.480 --> 39:15.880
So, 1703 is not a store?

39:17.000 --> 39:18.600
Officer Ran. I forgot.

39:18.680 --> 39:21.400
Room 1703 is the biggest.

39:21.480 --> 39:22.800
Mr. Song keeps it for himself.

39:24.720 --> 39:29.280
They say Mr. Song
keeps his mistress in 1703.

39:29.360 --> 39:30.320
Shush!

39:33.240 --> 39:35.920
Ma'am, have you seen him

39:36.960 --> 39:38.160
bringing anyone?

39:39.200 --> 39:42.800
But often, some flashy-dressed women

39:42.880 --> 39:44.680
come to get clothes altered.

39:45.400 --> 39:46.840
Guess what.

39:46.920 --> 39:50.280
The thing is, it's never
the same person twice.

39:53.520 --> 39:56.080
Ma'am, have you seen this woman?

39:57.400 --> 39:58.600
How can I remember?

39:58.680 --> 40:00.920
I do my best to avoid them. What bad luck.

40:02.960 --> 40:06.560
Don't you want to ask about 1703?

40:06.640 --> 40:07.680
Mr. Song is home.

40:09.200 --> 40:10.680
Song Qingsong is home?

40:10.760 --> 40:12.040
Yeah.

40:12.560 --> 40:15.840
That door squeaks whenever it opens.

40:15.920 --> 40:18.080
I would know if he comes out.

40:45.440 --> 40:47.560
What is this?

40:51.560 --> 40:52.480
Mr. Song.

40:53.520 --> 40:56.200
Are you home? I'm the property manager.

40:59.760 --> 41:01.040
Mr. Song.

41:02.560 --> 41:03.560
Mr. Song.

41:09.320 --> 41:10.160
Hello.

41:10.240 --> 41:11.880
Police, Nanshan Branch.

41:11.960 --> 41:13.560
I have some questions.

41:13.640 --> 41:15.560
I know you're home. Please open the door.

41:19.920 --> 41:20.960
Mr. Song.

41:25.360 --> 41:26.520
Are you Song Qingsong?

41:27.200 --> 41:30.360
No. I'm Mr. Song's secretary.

41:30.440 --> 41:31.720
I came to get some papers.

41:31.800 --> 41:33.240
What can I do for you?

41:36.120 --> 41:38.520
-Let me take a look.
-I'm afraid I can't.

41:39.960 --> 41:41.560
This is not my place.

41:41.640 --> 41:43.520
I don't have a say here.

41:44.520 --> 41:45.840
When is he coming back?

41:45.920 --> 41:48.960
Well… I'm not sure.

41:49.040 --> 41:52.360
He usually gets drunk at night
and sleeps here.

41:57.120 --> 41:59.600
Officer, he's in a hurry for these files.

41:59.680 --> 42:01.880
If you've got nothing else,
please head back.

42:04.240 --> 42:05.840
It's too hot. Can I have some water?

42:05.920 --> 42:06.800
The water is out.

42:07.720 --> 42:10.560
-Coke is fine, too.
-Coke is for me.

42:20.120 --> 42:21.120
Shit!

42:21.200 --> 42:22.760
This guy is a burglar.

42:22.840 --> 42:24.920
Ouch. Ma Qiang. Push.

42:25.000 --> 42:26.960
This guy is a burglar.

42:28.120 --> 42:29.560
-Lock the door.
-Okay.

42:37.960 --> 42:38.960
Go.

42:39.040 --> 42:41.960
Dad. What's the next move
of the horse stance side strike?

42:42.040 --> 42:44.080
Kick. Throat lock.

42:46.880 --> 42:48.440
Teach me again.

42:49.280 --> 42:52.680
You're biting off more than you can chew.

42:55.880 --> 42:57.520
GOLDEN ROCK AUDIO SHOP OPENING

42:57.600 --> 42:59.760
The rock singers all look weird.

43:00.360 --> 43:02.120
Rocking and rolling.
How can they look good?

43:03.200 --> 43:05.360
What a heavy bag for a third grader.

43:06.200 --> 43:09.960
The teachers and parents
are oppressing children.

43:10.040 --> 43:12.080
Dad. Are we going to Grandma's?

43:12.160 --> 43:13.480
Do you like Grandma's place, kiddo?

43:13.560 --> 43:14.600
Yeah, of course.

43:14.680 --> 43:16.480
She has Hua and Huang.

43:16.560 --> 43:18.760
We can catch mice in the yard.

43:19.280 --> 43:20.280
Then let's go to Grandma's.

43:22.080 --> 43:23.920
-Dad, you're the best.
-Get in.

43:29.120 --> 43:31.920
Got a lead. Return to the unit. Ran.

43:38.080 --> 43:41.560
Xiaohe. We won't go to Grandma's yet.

43:42.160 --> 43:44.400
Dad. You're going back on your word again.

43:45.600 --> 43:48.640
Want to see where Dad works?

43:48.720 --> 43:49.960
The police station?

43:50.040 --> 43:52.240
Are there a lot of bad people
locked up there?

43:52.320 --> 43:53.240
Are you afraid?

43:53.320 --> 43:56.040
Not at all. My dad catches bad guys.

43:56.840 --> 43:57.720
Alright, sit tight.

44:07.480 --> 44:09.680
Slow down. What's the rush?

44:10.240 --> 44:11.640
Officer Zhang. Officer Li.

44:11.720 --> 44:12.640
You clown.

44:12.720 --> 44:14.280
You're kind of a regular here.

44:14.360 --> 44:15.360
Can't bear to leave, huh?

44:16.320 --> 44:18.720
-Thanks. You helped us a lot.
-No problem.

44:22.280 --> 44:24.960
I'd like to borrow the loot.

44:25.880 --> 44:26.760
Huh?

44:30.560 --> 44:33.000
Dad. What did he do?

44:34.240 --> 44:36.400
Officer He. Long time no see.

44:36.480 --> 44:38.000
Keep your mouth shut.

44:38.080 --> 44:39.440
Just saying hi.

44:39.520 --> 44:40.800
He's a pickpocket.

44:40.880 --> 44:42.360
I've caught him before.

44:43.040 --> 44:44.560
Does he really pick pockets?

44:46.440 --> 44:48.800
Xiaohe. Say hi to Uncle Ran.

44:48.880 --> 44:49.840
Hello, Xiaohe.

44:51.720 --> 44:55.080
You're Uncle Ran, the graduate from PPSUC?

44:56.120 --> 44:57.640
You're pretty well-informed.

44:57.720 --> 45:01.560
My mom told my dad to learn from you.

45:01.640 --> 45:03.240
Don't talk nonsense.

45:03.320 --> 45:04.680
How am I talking nonsense?

45:04.760 --> 45:07.480
My mom also said
that you should butter up Uncle Ran

45:07.560 --> 45:09.560
so he can promote you
once he becomes an official.

45:09.640 --> 45:11.320
Finished your summer break homework?

45:14.800 --> 45:17.360
Xiaohe. Uncle Ran and I
have things to talk about.

45:17.440 --> 45:18.800
Go to the office. Finish your homework.

45:18.880 --> 45:21.040
No. I’m going to play
basketball in the yard.

45:21.120 --> 45:22.280
Hey you!

45:22.360 --> 45:25.320
Uncle Ran. Come play when you're done.

45:25.400 --> 45:26.520
What a kid…

45:29.240 --> 45:30.960
Right, He. Song Qingsong…

45:31.040 --> 45:33.240
I've figured out what to do about him.

45:33.320 --> 45:34.760
Let's wait for him outside
the cement factory.

45:34.840 --> 45:36.120
-Once he comes out…
-No.

45:36.200 --> 45:37.920
He will be here soon.

45:39.080 --> 45:40.000
Huh?
